oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: 4 Big Acts Celebrating Earth Day
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Me Phi Me (Musical group); Mosser, Jonell; Carl, Max; Split fountain printing; Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black and split fountain, green to yellow to orange, on white) announcing 4 Big Acts Celebrating Earth Day featuring Reality Salad, Me Phi Me, Jonell Mosser, and Max Carl and Big Dance at 328 Performance Hall in Nashville, Tennessee on April 22. Poster features a woodcut of a band and conductor.
